00:00:38.880 --> 00:00:43.520
"Out-of-the-box compatibility with our legacy infrastructure is exceptional."

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.680
"Highly recommended for critical work."

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:49.360
"Since provisioning lui.z into our organizational cluster,

00:00:49.360 --> 00:00:51.840
I actually get to sleep through the night."

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:53.840
"The failover capabilities are flawless."

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:56.320
"Never seen anyone smash as much coffee.

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:58.560
It's triple-shot flat whites constant."

00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:01.280
